{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B10%2C5%2C1%2C0%2C1%5D%2C%5B10%2C5%2C1%2C0%2C1%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><p data-lake-id=\"f575d5292f3994147a517be2f55af13e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ol start=\"1\" data-lake-id=\"07db8432f52142366d299a8f04a6cdd2\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"793ae4d71a2b0c12597642069b5e07cb\">CSS：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"366e2f2a88ef8ef715da954abba35a4a\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"fa40f8ed029325e0b85c679dce4bc101\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"666d2022cc7d0e680927a569e04df515\">BFC容器、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"b3db59b042a3ca191fde46a23be8e5f5\">居中方式、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"30870338b709caed229736ffd1b50a29\">flex布局  ✅</li></ol></ol><ol start=\"2\" data-lake-id=\"cd2c68b5da43d1f28dba99bfeebf1602\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"d605e0bf58d47b127760350ccffa1215\">JS：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"f94503c01aaa5449827a798f28d594cf\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"f8aca95032f2312bf5e49ccff3c2aae6\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"7a02c2c23e815d486b573ffd899b0e18\">原型链、</li><li data-lake-id=\"b2f6c7044fad43f9c04be8321e8cc28f\">函数执行栈、</li><li data-lake-id=\"81202d16687f1bff324a0d4a95b5c672\">闭包、<a href=\"http://www.imooc.com/read/70/article/1610\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.imooc.com/read/70/article/1610</a></li><li data-lake-id=\"52b0b6693232fd8b0c93e0af20087b18\">this、</li><li data-lake-id=\"318f9dd7e62a4cd24e1e8b6d2ae4a72c\"><span>JS eventloop机制 </span><span>✅</span></li></ol></ol><ol start=\"3\" data-lake-id=\"5a15bc7636ceac6cc3557a0184b7aeaf\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"a9ac4767740ddac50b3f29cc90ce40dd\">手写JS代码：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"3e6b637706e88521a0eef21b04f4eec2\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"d7e322617071d1bf9da7002fbd249f6f\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"59c4b8239a87efcce6ca9598543dfb37\">防抖/节流、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"6387c6c79481d143c4738bfc31ba4e2b\">Promise.all、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"0598418abd5b739aba4c64f2ac13b76a\">选择、插入、快排/归并排序 <span>✅</span></li></ol></ol><ol start=\"4\" data-lake-id=\"304f13e6fa9629325ec13c02d738e9da\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"68ca3348af3ce9eba10177ee75fe3bfc\">react：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"307deb65fe2a5ce944ad91459ce3276f\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"f3082ccb8481cd119746dda33cfb6fdc\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"0984da6740b7d2bb551051c31a10b559\">fiber原理、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"bcb054bd0470231fc63709f944fe20d5\">hooks原理、</li><li data-lake-id=\"302368414aecfc07b8ec25c406692365\">diff算法原理<strong> </strong><span>✅</span></li></ol></ol><ol start=\"5\" data-lake-id=\"86c1988f663f6276e1d5b2e5bdfb0d6c\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"38d04e25fa71d63d430211b5ea15f548\">网络：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"d138f2925fc2144ec2d90c4582d0e5db\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"5dc3ffcf44d2bc1e7d42e30e221f452f\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"c962e0730e43be073c805cffe3975e54\"><span>https原理、</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"9d8dab26496c22c3ea1c44eb135cc16a\">DNS解析流程、</li><li data-lake-id=\"ed4637fe06ce9c9eded89994d2bf36e7\">CDN原理、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"5dc529fec9f0975808c3b8aec0762683\">TCP/UDP协议、</li><li data-lake-id=\"bb95c9fa76c7508da9a8e0a984f4b746\">三次握手四次挥手过程、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"388512cb966ecb1deff3729d672ea56c\">HTTP1.1/2区别、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"e9d97f56e0f2bdd84d02f6361c3a0642\">各状态码表达含义</li></ol></ol><ol start=\"6\" data-lake-id=\"80ce7c2d8655207054e42ccaf0191385\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"78c52dcbf939984bc6b76e8ad6510c35\">浏览器原理：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"0bad7a9ed087b60c3627d76352b290c0\" lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ol data-lake-id=\"a372a1d345f1ff5bee56c520ffe6a555\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li data-lake-id=\"6e2b4b1ad46718a857885015fb0dabeb\">从HTML到完整页面展示全流程， <span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"f7dd6d05cba6e0762d6cdb27c344d7ee\"><span>流/重绘/合成 </span></li></ol></ol><ol start=\"7\" data-lake-id=\"cd0ed0dbc0c59a66f41df674d72b61f1\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"d15792f0dd0ae9fe44173d1b81ed07b6\">v8(V型8缸发动机)：GC机制</li><li data-lake-id=\"28d5ac7054e3defc94113559bce99e9c\">缓存：强缓存与协商缓存完整过程</li><li data-lake-id=\"3492f33dd96d4f319ec324992c14f49e\">跨域：成因、注意事项及解决方案</li><li data-lake-id=\"bae9dc7706cb2e9f1e4e8ce4fea7f774\">node：express/koa中间件原理，SSR原理</li><li data-lake-id=\"3ea1ac4f572c2ecfaa726d9fe1a9025d\">web安全：xss与csrf，原理及防范手段</li><li data-lake-id=\"691463066a6c2b6384af25703e2c9033\">前端工程化：webpack优化策略，vite优点</li><li data-lake-id=\"ddf0a07006bd4b2513ac2786703bbe27\">性能优化：常见性能瓶颈、优化手段，如何检测首屏时间并提升首屏速度</li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"3c8b0884ecb4d9145873645470c6b651\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"450f02620c7e1082ee34a8c4f1f9b11e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">其它：TS、移动端适配、flutter/RN/weex等native开发方式</p><p data-lake-id=\"3441368e53adb8dc12c4231a1281b8be\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"41f9399369d7262e7941b014050bee30\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">1.基本vue的api使用，用vue实战一个spa &nbsp;<a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.vuejs.org/index.html</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"da13ed0c61f816982acd941edd4852ad\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">2.熟悉浏览器history的api &nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/history\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/history</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"49d8fdccadb7afc741ada9aa11c16099\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">3.熟悉发布订阅的设计模式 &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ZZB_Bin/article/details/80229456\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/ZZB_Bin/article/details/80229456</a>（争取自己用js实现一个）</p><p data-lake-id=\"ad48523fa01d7b3d473e50fc5ecca90a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">4.熟悉什么是AST抽象语法树 <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32189701\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32189701</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"447e587ddd02990b6838822bd0b27f50\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">5.熟悉js的事件循环 微任务宏任务 &nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/EventLoop\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/EventLoop</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"aecde7ddfa3e3bc28854f4027101990a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_DOM_API/Microtask_guide\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_DOM_API/Microtask_guide</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"26a947af33faf3f8ddd9d3621069dbef\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">6.react源码预习：<a href=\"https://lilixikun.github.io/react/API.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://lilixikun.github.io/react/API.html</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"e8f601cddf96fba497812affd1038f0e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"cb3387d61f58cc7325edd1f761f97f0a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c65a72fa75341f482a1f74e59dc68fda\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"a9531ee8f6df935b95de26558a65ad59\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">swc</p><p data-lake-id=\"0b2ff76b79ba54e995374a67068a763a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">esbuild</p><p data-lake-id=\"dce4b8cd97fe64803f16d002cd7ee934\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">tree shaing</p><p data-lake-id=\"77743e229b10257141ae3b3412c817bd\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">魔法注释</p><p data-lake-id=\"78fcac2a5b2cac1259aeff76972bf463\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">浏览器支持查询： <a href=\"https://caniuse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://caniuse.com/</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"3184757e8d1d0846993a13ff0cf5ff8e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"f6a4616b957049c6806a348abb9e5104\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"b4b9f316046f7f943282526fc834ba33\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">webpack&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;cli.installed&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;runcli&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;wepack-cli&nbsp;-&gt;</p><p data-lake-id=\"0ff617f495d687abf452d033ebf24171\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">-&gt;&nbsp;v8-compile-cache&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;验证核心的参数&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;compiler&nbsp;=&nbsp;webpack()</p><p data-lake-id=\"effaa312d3ceb7cd3554c5b37bf610f3\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">[compiler]是整个webpack的核心&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;plugin.apply(compiler)</p><p data-lake-id=\"f7d3e3dad7eab5b13566e61812d0d9fd\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">-&gt;&nbsp;compiler.hooks.run.【tap】&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;Compiler.js</p><p data-lake-id=\"a97e69fdf120e6248641a431fcce8732\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">-&gt;compilation&nbsp;每一次编译结果</p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"traditional\" /><p data-lake-id=\"f575d5292f3994147a517be2f55af13e\"><br /></p><ol start=\"1\" data-lake-id=\"07db8432f52142366d299a8f04a6cdd2\"><li data-lake-id=\"793ae4d71a2b0c12597642069b5e07cb\">CSS：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"fa40f8ed029325e0b85c679dce4bc101\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"666d2022cc7d0e680927a569e04df515\">BFC容器、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"b3db59b042a3ca191fde46a23be8e5f5\">居中方式、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"30870338b709caed229736ffd1b50a29\">flex布局  ✅</li></ol><ol start=\"2\" data-lake-id=\"cd2c68b5da43d1f28dba99bfeebf1602\"><li data-lake-id=\"d605e0bf58d47b127760350ccffa1215\">JS：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"f8aca95032f2312bf5e49ccff3c2aae6\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"7a02c2c23e815d486b573ffd899b0e18\">原型链、</li><li data-lake-id=\"b2f6c7044fad43f9c04be8321e8cc28f\">函数执行栈、</li><li data-lake-id=\"81202d16687f1bff324a0d4a95b5c672\">闭包、<a href=\"http://www.imooc.com/read/70/article/1610\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.imooc.com/read/70/article/1610</a></li><li data-lake-id=\"52b0b6693232fd8b0c93e0af20087b18\">this、</li><li data-lake-id=\"318f9dd7e62a4cd24e1e8b6d2ae4a72c\"><span>JS eventloop机制 </span><span>✅</span></li></ol><ol start=\"3\" data-lake-id=\"5a15bc7636ceac6cc3557a0184b7aeaf\"><li data-lake-id=\"a9ac4767740ddac50b3f29cc90ce40dd\">手写JS代码：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"d7e322617071d1bf9da7002fbd249f6f\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"59c4b8239a87efcce6ca9598543dfb37\">防抖/节流、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"6387c6c79481d143c4738bfc31ba4e2b\">Promise.all、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"0598418abd5b739aba4c64f2ac13b76a\">选择、插入、快排/归并排序 <span>✅</span></li></ol><ol start=\"4\" data-lake-id=\"304f13e6fa9629325ec13c02d738e9da\"><li data-lake-id=\"68ca3348af3ce9eba10177ee75fe3bfc\">react：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"f3082ccb8481cd119746dda33cfb6fdc\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"0984da6740b7d2bb551051c31a10b559\">fiber原理、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"bcb054bd0470231fc63709f944fe20d5\">hooks原理、</li><li data-lake-id=\"302368414aecfc07b8ec25c406692365\">diff算法原理<strong> </strong><span>✅</span></li></ol><ol start=\"5\" data-lake-id=\"86c1988f663f6276e1d5b2e5bdfb0d6c\"><li data-lake-id=\"38d04e25fa71d63d430211b5ea15f548\">网络：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"5dc3ffcf44d2bc1e7d42e30e221f452f\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"c962e0730e43be073c805cffe3975e54\"><span>https原理、</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"9d8dab26496c22c3ea1c44eb135cc16a\">DNS解析流程、</li><li data-lake-id=\"ed4637fe06ce9c9eded89994d2bf36e7\">CDN原理、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"5dc529fec9f0975808c3b8aec0762683\">TCP/UDP协议、</li><li data-lake-id=\"bb95c9fa76c7508da9a8e0a984f4b746\">三次握手四次挥手过程、<span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"388512cb966ecb1deff3729d672ea56c\">HTTP1.1/2区别、<span>✅<cursor /></span></li><li data-lake-id=\"e9d97f56e0f2bdd84d02f6361c3a0642\">各状态码表达含义</li></ol><ol start=\"6\" data-lake-id=\"80ce7c2d8655207054e42ccaf0191385\"><li data-lake-id=\"78c52dcbf939984bc6b76e8ad6510c35\">浏览器原理：</li></ol><ol data-lake-id=\"a372a1d345f1ff5bee56c520ffe6a555\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li data-lake-id=\"6e2b4b1ad46718a857885015fb0dabeb\">从HTML到完整页面展示全流程， <span>✅</span></li><li data-lake-id=\"f7dd6d05cba6e0762d6cdb27c344d7ee\"><span>流/重绘/合成 </span></li></ol><ol start=\"7\" data-lake-id=\"cd0ed0dbc0c59a66f41df674d72b61f1\"><li data-lake-id=\"d15792f0dd0ae9fe44173d1b81ed07b6\">v8(V型8缸发动机)：GC机制</li><li data-lake-id=\"28d5ac7054e3defc94113559bce99e9c\">缓存：强缓存与协商缓存完整过程</li><li data-lake-id=\"3492f33dd96d4f319ec324992c14f49e\">跨域：成因、注意事项及解决方案</li><li data-lake-id=\"bae9dc7706cb2e9f1e4e8ce4fea7f774\">node：express/koa中间件原理，SSR原理</li><li data-lake-id=\"3ea1ac4f572c2ecfaa726d9fe1a9025d\">web安全：xss与csrf，原理及防范手段</li><li data-lake-id=\"691463066a6c2b6384af25703e2c9033\">前端工程化：webpack优化策略，vite优点</li><li data-lake-id=\"ddf0a07006bd4b2513ac2786703bbe27\">性能优化：常见性能瓶颈、优化手段，如何检测首屏时间并提升首屏速度</li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"3c8b0884ecb4d9145873645470c6b651\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"450f02620c7e1082ee34a8c4f1f9b11e\">其它：TS、移动端适配、flutter/RN/weex等native开发方式</p><p data-lake-id=\"3441368e53adb8dc12c4231a1281b8be\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"41f9399369d7262e7941b014050bee30\">1.基本vue的api使用，用vue实战一个spa  <a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.vuejs.org/index.html</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"da13ed0c61f816982acd941edd4852ad\">2.熟悉浏览器history的api  <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/history\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/history</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"49d8fdccadb7afc741ada9aa11c16099\">3.熟悉发布订阅的设计模式    <a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ZZB_Bin/article/details/80229456\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/ZZB_Bin/article/details/80229456</a>（争取自己用js实现一个）</p><p data-lake-id=\"ad48523fa01d7b3d473e50fc5ecca90a\">4.熟悉什么是AST抽象语法树 <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32189701\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32189701</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"447e587ddd02990b6838822bd0b27f50\">5.熟悉js的事件循环 微任务宏任务  <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/EventLoop\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/EventLoop</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"aecde7ddfa3e3bc28854f4027101990a\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_DOM_API/Microtask_guide\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_DOM_API/Microtask_guide</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"26a947af33faf3f8ddd9d3621069dbef\">6.react源码预习：<a href=\"https://lilixikun.github.io/react/API.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://lilixikun.github.io/react/API.html</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"e8f601cddf96fba497812affd1038f0e\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"cb3387d61f58cc7325edd1f761f97f0a\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"c65a72fa75341f482a1f74e59dc68fda\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"a9531ee8f6df935b95de26558a65ad59\">swc</p><p data-lake-id=\"0b2ff76b79ba54e995374a67068a763a\">esbuild</p><p data-lake-id=\"dce4b8cd97fe64803f16d002cd7ee934\">tree shaing</p><p data-lake-id=\"77743e229b10257141ae3b3412c817bd\">魔法注释</p><p data-lake-id=\"78fcac2a5b2cac1259aeff76972bf463\">浏览器支持查询： <a href=\"https://caniuse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://caniuse.com/</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"3184757e8d1d0846993a13ff0cf5ff8e\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"f6a4616b957049c6806a348abb9e5104\"><br /></p><p data-lake-id=\"b4b9f316046f7f943282526fc834ba33\">webpack -&gt; cli.installed -&gt; runcli -&gt; wepack-cli -&gt;</p><p data-lake-id=\"0ff617f495d687abf452d033ebf24171\">-&gt; v8-compile-cache -&gt; 验证核心的参数 -&gt; compiler = webpack()</p><p data-lake-id=\"effaa312d3ceb7cd3554c5b37bf610f3\">[compiler]是整个webpack的核心 -&gt; plugin.apply(compiler)</p><p data-lake-id=\"f7d3e3dad7eab5b13566e61812d0d9fd\">-&gt; compiler.hooks.run.【tap】 -&gt; Compiler.js</p><p data-lake-id=\"a97e69fdf120e6248641a431fcce8732\">-&gt;compilation 每一次编译结果</p>","body_dr